## Educational and Personal Use Notice

This software is provided for educational purposes and personal use. While the
MIT license permits commercial use, this project is primarily intended for:

1. **Educational Use**: Learning about code indexing, semantic search, and
   AI-assisted development tools
2. **Personal Projects**: Enhancing productivity in individual or small-team
   development workflows
3. **Research**: Academic study of code analysis techniques and developer tools

### Attribution

If you use this software in educational materials, research papers, or derived
works, please provide attribution to the original Archimyst project:

```
ArchCode Terminal CLI by Archimyst
https://github.com/hritvikgupta/Archimyst
https://www.archimyst.com
```

