### Privacy and Data

This software processes code locally and may transmit data to third-party AI
providers when configured to do so. Users are responsible for:
- Ensuring compliance with their organization's data policies
- Protecting sensitive code and API keys
- Understanding the privacy policies of any integrated AI providers

